and schedule some time to get away from it all. visas[edit] do you need a visa? visa-exempt bhutan nepal tourist visa on arrival (tvoa) at the airports in chennai, mumbai, delhi, kolkata, kochi, bangalore, hyderabad and trivandrum, for a stay of up to 30 days. it can take one to two hours to process the application once you have arrived at the airport. the tvoa costs 3600 rupees (60 usd), is valid for a single entry and is not extendible. the airport immigration will only accept rupees so you can get your money exchanged overseas or they will escort you 